<body>
  <h1>Add Calendar to Google Calendar</h1>
  <p>Tap the button below to add the calendar to your Google Calendar app on iOS.</p>
  <button onclick="redirectToCalendar()">Add to Calendar</button>
  <div class="instructions">
    <p><strong>If the button doesn't work:</strong></p>
    <ol>
      <li>Open the <strong>Google Calendar app</strong>.</li>
      <li>Tap the <strong>menu</strong> (three lines, top left).</li>
      <li>Go to <strong>Settings</strong> > <strong>Add calendar</strong> > <strong>From URL</strong>.</li>
      <li>Paste this calendar ID: <br><strong>c301166a5c6178072d2c381bdf7a7bd7120f30c59dca4a84111eba6d8fb7dc95@group.calendar.google.com</strong></li>
      <li>Tap <strong>Add calendar</strong>.</li>
      <li>Return to the main view, tap the menu, and ensure the calendar is checked.</li>
    </ol>
    <p>Alternatively, open this link in Safari: <br><a href="https://calendar.google.com/calendar/u/3?cid=Y180YzMwMTE2NmE1YzYxNzgwNzJkMmMzODFiZGZhN2JkNzEyMGYzMGM1OWRjYTRhODQxMTFlYmE2ZDhmYjdkYzk1QGdyb3VwLmNhbGVuZGFyLmdvb2dsZS5jb20">Add Calendar in Browser</a></p>
  </div>

  <script>
    function redirectToCalendar() {
      const calendarId = 'c301166a5c6178072d2c381bdf7a7bd7120f30c59dca4a84111eba6d8fb7dc95@group.calendar.google.com';
      const originalUrl = 'https://calendar.google.com/calendar/u/3?cid=Y180YzMwMTE2NmE1YzYxNzgwNzJkMmMzODFiZGZhN2JkNzEyMGYzMGM1OWRjYTRhODQxMTFlYmE2ZDhmYjdkYzk1QGdyb3VwLmNhbGVuZGFyLmdvb2dsZS5jb20';
      
      // Attempt to open Google Calendar app
      window.location.href = `googlecalendar://?cid=${encodeURIComponent(calendarId)}`;

      // Fallback to web URL after 1.5 seconds if app doesn't open
      setTimeout(() => {
        window.location.href = originalUrl;
      }, 1500);
    }
  </script>
